<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="distinction-n">distinction <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'stɪŋkʃn/    美 /dɪ'stɪŋkʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>区别；差别；不同：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should <strong>draw / make a distinction between</strong> right <strong>and</strong> wrong.
我们应该明辨是非。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[常用单数] 特点；特性：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the chief distinction of Chinese poetry
中国诗歌的主要特征</p></div></div>